I've been reading more these days, probably explaining the need for reading glasses.

In the spirit of Derek Silvers, I've decided to starting actively taking [notes](https://gist.github.com/paulywill/7f652249516107a42ba839267f3341fb) promptly after finishing a book to keep my impressions and takeaways fresh.

